therefore, they institute the Annual Purge plan from 7 pm on March 20 to 7 am the next day

00:00:34.335 --> 00:00:39.583
in other words, during these 12 hours, Americans can do anything without being punished by law

00:00:39.711 --> 00:00:41.600
killing is no exception

