as expected, the rioters who are unfamiliar with the area 

00:10:15.049 --> 00:10:19.529
are besieged as soon as they get up the hill, and immediately suffer heavy casualties

00:10:20.041 --> 00:10:24.073
some rioters are shot dead by a bolt before they could see anyone

00:10:24.393 --> 00:10:26.825
seeing his companions all die one after another

00:10:27.017 --> 00:10:30.409
Captain takes advantage of the chaos to snatch away Adela 

00:10:30.537 --> 00:10:33.929
little does he know that Juan and Dylan are hidden right behind him 

